head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  title Entrega de clase 6
  script(src='https://cdn.tailwindcss.com')
  script.
    tailwind.config = {
    theme: {
    extend: {
    colors: {
    primary: '#da373d',
    }
    }
    }
    }
  style.
    body {
    height: 100vh;
    background: #f4f4f4;
    }
main
  section.formulario.w-full.min-h-screen.flex.flex-col.gap-8.justify-center.items-center
    article
      h1.w-full.font-bold.text-4xl.text-purple-600 Formulario con Pug
    article
      form(action='http://localhost:8080/productos' method='post' enctype='multipart/form-data')
        .max-w-md.w-full.space-y-8.p-10.bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.z-10
          .grid.gap-8.grid-cols-1
            .flex.flex-col
              .flex.flex-col.items-center(class='sm:flex-row')
                h2.font-semibold.text-lg.mr-auto Formulario de carga de producto
                .w-full.mt-3(class='sm:w-auto sm:ml-auto sm:mt-0')
              .mt-5
                .form
                  .flex-row.w-full.text-xs(class='md:flex md:space-x-4')
                    .flex-row.w-full.text-xs(class='md:flex md:space-x-4')
                      .mb-3.space-y-2.w-full.text-xs
                        label.font-semibold.text-gray-600.py-2
                          | Titulo 
                          abbr(title='required') *
                        input#integration_title.appearance-none.block.w-full.bg-grey-lighter.text-grey-darker.border.border-grey-lighter.rounded-lg.h-10.px-4(placeholder='Angular JS' required='required' type='text' name='integration[title]')
                        p.text-red.text-xs.hidden Este campo es necesario.
                    .mb-3.space-y-2.w-full.text-xs
                      label.font-semibold.text-gray-600.py-2
                        | Precio 
                        abbr(title='required') *
                      input#integration_price.appearance-none.block.w-full.bg-grey-lighter.text-grey-darker.border.border-grey-lighter.rounded-lg.h-10.px-4(placeholder='0,00' required='required' type='number' name='integration[price]')
                      p.text-red.text-xs.hidden Este campo es necesario.
                  .mb-3.space-y-2.w-full.text-xs
                    label.font-semibold.text-gray-600.py-2
                      | URL de imagen 
                      abbr(title='required') *
                    .flex.flex-wrap.items-stretch.w-full.mb-4.relative
                      .flex
                        span.flex.items-center.leading-normal.bg-grey-lighter.border-1.rounded-r-none.border.border-r-0.border-blue-300.px-3.whitespace-no-wrap.text-grey-dark.text-sm.w-12.h-10.bg-blue-300.justify-center.items-center.text-xl.rounded-lg.text-white
                          svg.h-6.w-6(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' fill='none' viewbox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor')
                            path(stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z')
                      input#integration_imageurl.flex-shrink.flex-grow.flex-auto.leading-normal.w-px.flex-1.border.border-l-0.h-10.border-grey-light.rounded-lg.rounded-l-none.px-3.relative(type='text' class='focus:border-blue focus:shadow' placeholder='https://' name='integration[imageurl]')
                  .mb-3.mt-4(class='md:space-y-2')
                    .flex.items-center
                      label
                        input#thumbnail.form-control.block.w-full.px-3.text-base.font-normal.text-gray-700.bg-white.bg-clip-padding.border.border-solid.border-gray-300.rounded.transition.ease-in-out.m-0(class='py-1.5 focus:text-gray-700 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-600 focus:outline-none' type='file' :accept='accept' name='thumbnail')
                  p.text-xs.text-red-500.text-right.my-6
                    | Los campos obligatorios est&aacute;n marcados con un
                    | asterisco 
                    abbr(title='Required field') *
                  .mt-5.text-right.flex.flex-col-reverse.gap-2(class='md:flex-row')
                    a.mb-2.mr-4.bg-white.px-5.py-2.text-center.text-sm.shadow-sm.font-medium.tracking-wider.border.text-gray-600.rounded-full(class='md:mb-0 md:mr-0 hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-100' href='/productos')
                      | Listado de productos
                    button.mb-2.bg-purple-400.px-5.py-2.text-sm.shadow-sm.font-medium.tracking-wider.text-white.rounded-full(class='md:mb-0 hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-purple-500' type='submit')
                      | Guardar producto